      • getYLabel

        public java.lang.String getYLabel​(boolean useSI)
        Return the Y-axis label for this engineering unit code. This corresponds to the descriptive label followed by the units label enclosed in parenthesis.
        Parameters:
        useSI - a true for the Y-Axis label with SI units; a false for the Y-Axis label with British units
        Returns:
        the Y-axis label
